task: frost-vault-integration (FROST slice 8)
owner: opus-autonomous
started: 2026-06-23
approach: FrostSigningClient extends the wallet RemoteSigningClient seam (in-house threshold
  counterpart to the remote walletVaultMpc* provider clients). Plugs straight into McpVault
  (kind=Mpc) — no new Vault impl needed. New module walletVaultMpcFrost dependsOn
  walletVaultMpc + cryptoFrost. FrostQuorum runs the FROST 2-round protocol over the signing subset.
